WEBVTT

00:41.145 --> 00:43.813
Friend! 


00:43.813 --> 00:46.000
Hey, Friend! 


00:47.568 --> 00:49.945
Friend! 


00:49.945 --> 00:52.000
Hey, Friend! 


01:01.290 --> 01:04.000
Friend! 


01:11.175 --> 01:14.000
Friend!


01:17.890 --> 01:19.933
What? 


01:19.933 --> 01:21.976
Who’s there?


01:21.977 --> 01:24.689
Friend, lend me three loaves, 


01:24.688 --> 01:27.356
because one of my friends 
has just come to me on a journey, 


01:27.357 --> 01:29.360
and I have nothing to offer him.


01:29.360 --> 01:31.987
Stop bothering me.


01:31.987 --> 01:32.570
No, no, no. 


01:32.570 --> 01:33.363
Wait! 
Wait! 


01:33.363 --> 01:34.113
Don’t go; 


01:34.113 --> 01:36.000
I beg you!


01:40.578 --> 01:42.623
The door is already locked. 


01:42.623 --> 01:45.166
My children are in bed. 


01:45.167 --> 01:46.877
Ugh! 


01:46.877 --> 01:48.879
I can’t get up. 


01:48.878 --> 01:51.340
It’s too late to give you anything.


01:51.340 --> 01:52.758
No, no! 


01:52.758 --> 01:54.000
Don’t go! 
No!


02:00.682 --> 02:02.685
Help me, please! 


02:02.685 --> 02:04.687
There is no one else! 


02:04.687 --> 02:07.000
Please!
Please!


02:12.485 --> 02:15.738
OK, OK. 


02:15.738 --> 02:40.826
I’m coming down.

